From b619c7ac21853558d08a40a31132950bfecc9383 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yafang Shao <laoar.shao@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 19 Dec 2024 10:34:50 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] net: remove get_task_comm() and print task comm directly
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: b619c7ac21853558d08a40a31132950bfecc9383
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Since task->comm is guaranteed to be NUL-terminated, we can print it
directly without the need to copy it into a separate buffer.  This
simplifies the code and avoids unnecessary operations.

Link: https://lkml.kernel.org/r/20241219023452.69907-4-laoar.shao@gmail.com
